        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository c5bc06fe-749f-42f0-a1ea-50e9e910277c).Image",
        "Description": "Patrick Achilles, Edgar Martin, and Daniel Fleischer are the leaders of a psychedelics ring going by the name &quot;Achilles&quot;. Recently they have been lacing their product with a potent neurotoxin, which has killed many. Interpol have been chasing them for a while but have made little progress. Achilles is currently undercover in a gang inside Berlin&apos;s Club Hölle. Interpol has requested a clean job with no civilian eliminations. Bonus payment will be awarded if Patrick is killed with lethal poison.",
